Following is a list of known bugs in [E]ntropy:

* Gross inefficiency in auto-arrange calls for thumbnailing.  This
  results in an O(n^2) inefficiency when loading directories.  
  Especially noticeable on slow hardware and large directories.

* Please, please email <alex@logisticchaos.com> with any SEGVs etc you
  find either from Entropy of EVFS


